WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:03.280 --> 00:00:06.400
Well, praise the Lord.

00:00:06.400 --> 00:00:13.430
Let me know when some people are showing up.

00:00:13.440 --> 00:00:48.150
I don't see it yet.

00:00:48.160 --> 00:00:49.760
Can you hear us?

00:00:49.760 --> 00:00:50.080
Yeah.

00:00:50.080 --> 00:00:51.360
Can you hear us?

00:00:51.360 --> 00:01:03.670
Is it loud and clear?

00:01:03.680 --> 00:01:04.799
Yep.

00:01:04.799 --> 00:01:07.611
They can hear us.

00:01:08.754 --> 00:01:11.451
Well, good evening, family.

00:01:11.451 --> 00:01:13.866
I won't say good morning today.

00:01:13.866 --> 00:01:15.216
Well, it's morning always somewhere.

00:01:15.216 --> 00:01:18.080
People say, "Why do you always say morning, Brandon?

00:01:18.080 --> 00:01:24.380
" I say, "Well, because it's morning somewhere, but good evening here in America.

00:01:24.790 --> 00:01:27.691
I feel in my heart we have much prayer to do.

00:01:27.691 --> 00:01:29.600
That's why I keep doing these lives.

00:01:29.600 --> 00:01:40.891
" You know, yesterday we did the live broadcast and we had 6,700 people praying with us at a time altogether within that time span.

00:01:41.280 --> 00:01:44.320
Braden said, "Dad, we had over 50,000 people praying.

00:01:44.320 --> 00:01:48.529
" And so we give all the glory to God for that.

00:01:48.529 --> 00:01:59.348
That all 50,000 of you at one point of that hour and a half, two hours, whatever it was, were praying for Charlie and his family and for our beautiful nation.

00:01:59.348 --> 00:02:05.959
So 50,000 people is a lot and I believe that many hands make light work.

00:02:05.959 --> 00:02:45.840
So my heart tonight is to come and pray as a family again for the capture of this man that did this heinous act, that we would help aid and assist in prayer the FBI, Homeland Security, and that there would be no rock, no cave, no cabin, no hotel room, nor any place at all that would be able to harbor this man, that he would be exposed and brought to justice swiftly, that this would not be a long drawn out process, that this would be a quick work.

00:02:45.840 --> 00:02:49.396
And so I already feel in my heart it's been too long.

00:02:49.396 --> 00:02:51.180
He needs to be brought to justice.

00:02:51.180 --> 00:03:00.819
But what we know in the spirit, as I have been praying over this all day today, is there's more than one.

00:03:02.469 --> 00:03:14.230
I know there was one shooter, but there is more than one person that has accompanied this man and that is involved with this.

00:03:14.230 --> 00:03:20.480
This is a lot deeper of a rabbit hole than what people realize.

00:03:20.480 --> 00:03:58.560
And so I was visited—and I'll say this carefully—I was visited by the Lord prophetically last night very late and He gave me the layout of a big scheme of things and He told me, "I will not allow you to put this on a public platform," what He has told me of a deeper, darker plan that is much more involved than what anyone could ever realize.

00:03:58.560 --> 00:04:18.280
And so whenever He was giving me so much detail, it was alarming, but at the same time, when you flow with the Spirit of the Lord, I just can't comprehend that kind of evil because His word is not evil.

00:04:19.760 --> 00:04:32.400
But when you see that people are demonically energized, you know, the Bible says we wrestle not against flesh and blood, but we wrestle against principalities and powers and spirits of wickedness in high places.

00:04:32.400 --> 00:04:34.112
We wrestle against demonic spirits.

00:04:36.640 --> 00:04:40.880
The principalities are working through personalities.

00:04:40.880 --> 00:04:48.960
So the people are just yielded vessels to a demonic spirit in any area.

00:04:49.210 --> 00:04:52.800
The devil will work through a personality, will work through a person.

00:04:52.800 --> 00:05:14.960
So that's what we're praying for tonight, to pray for confusion in the enemy's camp, that the plots and the plans of the wicked will be uncovered and the innocent lives will be spared.

00:05:14.960 --> 00:05:17.086
The innocent lives will be spared.

00:05:17.086 --> 00:05:18.996
We have a job to do.

00:05:18.996 --> 00:05:24.696
And that's why the Lord, I believe with all my heart, has raised us up for such a time as this.

00:05:24.696 --> 00:05:42.970
If you go back to one of my very first dreams that I had concerning YouTube, I was walking out of this building and it was a school cafeteria, and the Lord said, "I've called you to go in there and teach the children.

00:05:42.970 --> 00:05:45.051
I want you to teach them how to pray.

00:05:45.051 --> 00:05:50.639
" And out of disobedience, I walked out and I said, "I don't want to do this assignment.

00:05:50.639 --> 00:05:54.930
" And a whirlwind whipped me around and put me back at the school building.

00:05:54.930 --> 00:05:58.639
And He said, "Go teach My people to pray.

00:05:58.639 --> 00:06:00.017
" And I said, "Yes, Lord.

00:06:00.017 --> 00:06:08.129
" So I opened the door and I went in and there was a school auditorium and it was full of children that needed to learn how to pray.

00:06:08.129 --> 00:06:11.480
And He said, "Teach My people to pray.

00:06:11.480 --> 00:06:12.080
Go and pray.

00:06:13.280 --> 00:06:18.200
" So I took that assignment and that's what we've been doing.

00:06:18.540 --> 00:06:33.280
I saw the sky was split in half and the moon was turning into darkness and I could hear the air raid sirens blowing all around and I knew there was a storm coming.

00:06:33.280 --> 00:06:35.084
I knew there was a storm coming.

00:06:35.084 --> 00:06:53.1000
And the purpose of this channel, for this YouTube broadcast, is always to bring glory to God, to deflect always to Him, to always let you know that Brandon Biggs is just a vessel that is used by the Father and that anybody can do it.

00:06:53.1000 --> 00:06:55.260
Anybody can pray.

00:06:55.260 --> 00:07:00.800
I want you to know that He'll use you right where you are if you just say yes.

00:07:00.800 --> 00:07:08.416
And so the other part is to pray for us to change things as we see the days approaching.

00:07:08.416 --> 00:07:16.448
It's getting darker and darker, and Diana and I, we're so excited that you all would show up on a daily basis.

00:07:16.448 --> 00:07:24.266
And I'm not here to ramble, but I want you to be very serious and really engaged tonight.

00:07:24.266 --> 00:07:25.777
We have work to do.

00:07:25.777 --> 00:07:46.880
We saw through his sister in an email that when I told you all about Alabama—and I saw Alabama, you know, when you're talking in front of thousands of people, I try not to be, as I told Di, I said, "I'm more bold whenever I'm just talking to us and I'm making a video versus a live feed.

00:07:46.880 --> 00:08:03.093
" But when I saw Alabama and I saw the Crimson and I said, "There's a planned mass event at this place," and I saw Texas and I saw college campuses, to pray for college football games and tailgate parties.

00:08:03.093 --> 00:08:10.816
Then an article comes out today saying that there were threats made at these places.

00:08:11.280 --> 00:08:14.080
So we know we're on the right trail.

00:08:14.453 --> 00:08:17.339
We're hearing the news before the news has the news.

00:08:18.359 --> 00:08:37.919
And that's why we know we're on target praying for protection over our young people at the college campuses and at the tailgate parties because the Lord told me, He said, "Brandon, there'll be a great move of My Spirit, a great revival on college campuses around the United States.

00:08:37.919 --> 00:08:41.440
It will not just be—it'll be like popcorn.

00:08:41.440 --> 00:08:48.270
" That's whenever you take a pan of coconut oil and the popcorn seeds and you heat it up.

00:08:48.270 --> 00:09:04.971
You don't know which popcorn's going to pop first, but you just know in anticipation that the more you heat it up, the more the heat comes on those corn kernels, it's going to start to have a reaction and the popcorn's coming.

00:09:04.971 --> 00:09:08.996
So we know that what the Spirit of the Lord has warned us, He does.

00:09:08.996 --> 00:09:17.632
He told us, He said, "I'm going to do something unusual with My college campuses around the United States of America.

00:09:18.000 --> 00:09:26.000
" Specifically, there will be a major move of God, a major harvest of souls with the young people.

00:09:26.000 --> 00:09:27.870
And it would start with the young people.

00:09:27.870 --> 00:09:33.280
You'll start to see a major glory in the college campuses.

00:09:33.280 --> 00:09:49.320
So I'm believing even tonight that if you have young people at a college campus, that the fire starts with them, that they'll be spiritual—I'm not saying physical, but spiritual—arsonists, that they would set the fire.

00:09:49.320 --> 00:09:59.295
Like William Seymour: "Dip me in the kerosene of Thy Spirit, set my heart ablaze that I may burn for You.

00:09:59.295 --> 00:10:13.896
" I know that there has to be—there's that point in time where we're going to see that wave, the beginning of the fruit of this major revival throughout America and around the world.

00:10:13.896 --> 00:10:20.840
I know there's places that are seeing things, but we have not seen very much yet in America.

00:10:20.840 --> 00:10:25.200
And I believe that there's a great shaking to awaken.

00:10:25.200 --> 00:10:43.382
And from what I saw last night, I would love to be able to tell maybe the authorities, like the Secret Service or whatever, for the detail that I saw concerning an attack against America and in certain places.

00:10:43.382 --> 00:10:52.000
I saw more about the ten cities, great detail about the ten cities last night.

00:10:52.000 --> 00:10:59.080
And this was very heavy and I prayed and interceded for this for a long time.

00:10:59.080 --> 00:11:02.959
And so that's what we're going to pray over tonight.

00:11:03.279 --> 00:11:12.959
But our main priority is to pray for this man and all the people who helped him to be brought to justice quickly.

00:11:12.959 --> 00:11:13.399
Okay.

00:11:13.399 --> 00:11:14.990
So y'all want to go tubing?

00:11:14.990 --> 00:11:17.420
I'm not going to—I don't have anything else other than that.

00:11:17.420 --> 00:11:19.343
I've dumped out for the last several days.

00:11:19.343 --> 00:11:28.471
And I told Diana, I go, 'I've got to get refreshed, but at the same time, I feel an urgency to pray.

00:11:28.471 --> 00:11:32.160
' So, how many people are here?

00:11:32.160 --> 00:11:34.000
2,600.

00:11:34.000 --> 00:11:34.377
Okay.

00:11:34.377 --> 00:11:36.263
You can take communion.

00:11:36.263 --> 00:11:37.480
We're going to take communion.

00:11:37.480 --> 00:11:41.554
I never go into the river until I take communion first.

00:11:41.554 --> 00:11:47.360
You know me, I always make sure I cover all my bases.

00:11:47.360 --> 00:11:50.020
And so, Father, we just lift up the body before you.

00:11:50.020 --> 00:11:54.067
We thank you, Lord, that you were wounded for our transgressions.

00:11:54.067 --> 00:11:55.880
You were bruised for our iniquities.

00:11:55.880 --> 00:12:01.920
The chastisement of our peace was upon you, and with your stripes, we are healed.

00:12:01.920 --> 00:12:06.053
And we believe we receive everything that you have for us.

00:12:06.053 --> 00:12:08.050
We will lack no good thing, Lord.

00:12:08.050 --> 00:12:13.588
And we are healed in our flesh, in our minds, in our bodies, everything.

00:12:13.588 --> 00:12:16.213
We're made whole because of this body.

00:12:16.213 --> 00:12:27.456
You took it all on the cross for us to walk in victory over every area of our life—mentally, physically, financially, all of it.

00:12:27.456 --> 00:12:30.667
You took it for us to have an abundant life.

00:12:30.667 --> 00:12:37.324
And I believe, Father, that I receive that abundant life right now by faith, that I will lack nothing.

00:12:37.324 --> 00:12:38.980
I will lack no good thing.

00:12:39.240 --> 00:12:41.703
I will walk in the abundant believing.

00:12:41.703 --> 00:12:45.840
I'm a believing believer who walks in the abundance in Jesus' name.

00:12:45.840 --> 00:12:52.400
And we take this body, and we thank you, Lord, that you died for us and you rose again on that third day.

00:12:52.400 --> 00:12:58.129
And Father, I thank you that you're making intercession for us and you're seated at the right hand of the Father.

00:12:58.129 --> 00:13:00.620
I give you all the glory, honor, and praise.

00:13:00.620 --> 00:13:03.920
Father, we take this body in Jesus' name.

00:13:03.920 --> 00:13:04.880
Amen.

00:13:04.880 --> 00:13:08.320
Now, Lord, we thank you for the blood.

00:13:08.320 --> 00:13:12.000
And I plead the blood of Jesus all around my house.

00:13:12.000 --> 00:13:21.973
I plead the blood of Jesus all around my car, my finances, over my children, over my wife, over even our dogs.

00:13:21.973 --> 00:13:27.306
I plead the blood of Jesus over us, Father, for it never loses its power.

00:13:27.306 --> 00:13:31.839
And we make much of the blood, and the blood makes much of us.

00:13:31.839 --> 00:13:39.300
You said a thousand shall fall at our side and 10,000 at our right hand, but nothing shall come nigh us.

00:13:39.300 --> 00:13:44.903
I thank you, Lord, that every tongue that rises against us, we condemn it.

00:13:44.903 --> 00:13:52.939
Every word, every spell, every incantation, every chant, every voodoo, anything that tries to come against us in the spiritual realm falls to our feet.

00:13:52.939 --> 00:13:56.811
It does not bear fruit of any kind in the name of Jesus.

00:13:56.811 --> 00:14:00.500
We plead the blood of Jesus against it.

00:14:00.500 --> 00:14:02.350
And we thank you, Lord.

00:14:02.350 --> 00:14:07.320
I thank you, Lord, that whom God has blessed, no man can curse.

00:14:19.730 --> 00:14:19.980
I thank you for the blessing.

00:14:24.659 --> 00:14:24.949
The blessing and the favor of God follows me all the days.

00:14:26.925 --> 00:14:32.319
For goodness and mercy follow me all the days of my life, and I'll dwell in the house of the Lord forever.

00:14:32.319 --> 00:14:34.320
I thank you, Lord, for that blood.

00:14:34.320 --> 00:14:38.120
I thank you, Lord, that we make much of that blood tonight.

00:14:39.520 --> 00:14:39.760
We plead the blood of Jesus.

00:14:40.719 --> 00:14:51.040
We thank you, Lord, for angels and aid and assistance all around this house, all around us, that your angels are bearing us up in their hands lest we dash our foot against a stone.

00:14:51.040 --> 00:14:52.818
We thank you, Lord, for the blood.

00:14:52.818 --> 00:14:54.720
We thank you, Lord, for your covenant.

00:14:54.720 --> 00:15:06.679
We thank you, Lord, that we have much favor because of you, Lord, and we give you, Father, all the glory, honor, and praise.

00:15:06.679 --> 00:15:12.103
For you said, 'If I be lifted up, I'll draw all men unto you.

00:15:12.103 --> 00:15:30.936
' And I thank you, Father, in the name of Jesus, for that anointing, burden-removing, yoke-destroying power that flows on the inside of us in the mighty name of Jesus.

00:15:30.936 --> 00:15:32.659
Amen and amen.

00:15:39.120 --> 00:15:40.000
You take the blood.

00:15:44.800 --> 00:15:47.120
You say, 'Well, that's different.

00:15:47.120 --> 00:15:48.542
' Yep, that is.

00:15:48.542 --> 00:15:51.173
I take it in the way the Lord tells me to.

00:15:51.173 --> 00:15:53.180
So, I've just been reading over Ephesians.

00:15:53.440 --> 00:16:08.539
You really—I'm going to say this: in all the times of being serious about your covenant, serious about who you are in Christ, this is more of an alert time than ever before.

00:16:08.539 --> 00:16:16.925
This is a time like never before that you are awake and don't have a spiritual slumber about you.

00:16:16.925 --> 00:16:25.106
It's time for you to arise and shine, for the light has come and the glory of the Lord is risen upon you.

00:16:25.106 --> 00:16:34.380
It's time for you to be the salt in this earth like never before, wherever you are, being that voice similar to Charlie.

00:16:34.380 --> 00:16:42.000
We've watched a lot of his videos—Diana did today—of everything that that man said and what he stood for, and, man, it blesses.

00:16:42.000 --> 00:16:56.255
She said, 'Man, it challenges me when you see somebody who stood and died for the cause of Christ like a martyr, and you see what they meant to so many people and the impartation of wisdom that he had.

00:16:56.255 --> 00:16:57.311
' It was Holy Ghost-given.

00:17:03.680 --> 00:17:04.010
I'm telling you, that's not normal to be that witty.

00:17:12.036 --> 00:17:12.311
You know when the spirit of God is on somebody.

00:17:18.068 --> 00:17:18.445
And there are so many people criticizing in emails and things, saying, 'Brandon, you see so much.

00:17:18.445 --> 00:17:20.372
Why didn't you see this?

00:17:20.372 --> 00:17:27.600
If you truly have a gift and God shows you things, how come you didn't see this?

00:17:27.600 --> 00:17:33.344
' And I can only tell you that I only see in part, and I hear in part, and it's as the Spirit wills.

00:17:33.344 --> 00:17:35.280
I don't have control over it.

00:17:47.547 --> 00:17:47.960
And He shows me what I'm supposed to see for that day.

00:17:49.590 --> 00:17:53.250
And obviously, He did not see that I needed to see that.

00:17:53.250 --> 00:17:54.489
I'm not God.

00:17:59.097 --> 00:18:00.640
And I am telling you this: I am far from anything cool.

00:18:00.640 --> 00:18:09.031
I'm going to tell you, I'm only filled with and controlled by the Holy Ghost, like I pray you all are.

00:18:11.111 --> 00:18:15.938
And as I develop and I see things, I try to wrap my mind around it.

00:18:22.980 --> 00:18:24.620
I ask the Lord all the time, 'Lord, we could have been praying for him more.

00:18:36.048 --> 00:18:36.256
We could...

00:18:36.256 --> 00:18:37.640
' You take it personally.

00:18:37.640 --> 00:18:39.720
Lord, help us.

00:18:43.220 --> 00:18:43.730
I don't want to see a brother in the Lord die like that.

00:18:57.679 --> 00:18:57.919
I don't want to see anybody have a tragic event like that.

00:19:07.600 --> 00:19:07.776
But all I can tell you is that we live in a fallen world and sometimes things happen.

00:19:10.352 --> 00:19:18.392
And at the same time, it's like when people try to say to us, 'How come you didn't see Megan getting that shot and all that happened to her?

00:19:18.392 --> 00:19:28.937
' I said, 'That morning when I went to the doctor's office and they gave it to her, I heard the Spirit of the Lord yelling, "Do not do it!

00:19:28.937 --> 00:19:36.320
" But I disobeyed out of fear of that virus versus trusting that God was telling me not to do something.

00:19:36.320 --> 00:19:39.100
' I don't know where He was.

00:19:40.650 --> 00:19:41.716
I don't know where anybody is when something tragic happens.

00:19:41.716 --> 00:19:42.827
That's not my place to judge.

00:19:42.827 --> 00:19:50.639
But I'm going to tell you this: I believe that God is an ever-present help in a time of need, and we stay on the Lord's side even when we don't understand it.

00:19:52.800 --> 00:19:53.280
We don't go, 'Well, God did this, He did that.

00:19:53.280 --> 00:19:57.467
' No, I don't believe God's a kill, steal, and destroy God.

00:19:57.467 --> 00:20:07.549
Regardless of what we go through and how hard things seem to be sometimes, God is a good God and the devil is a bad devil.

00:20:26.320 --> 00:20:26.720
So, there's a lot of people asking, 'Brandon, why?

00:20:26.720 --> 00:20:27.520
Why?

00:20:27.520 --> 00:20:28.040
Why?

00:20:28.040 --> 00:20:29.600
' I don't know why.

00:20:30.520 --> 00:20:30.750
I don't know why.

00:20:30.750 --> 00:20:32.217
And that's a good enough answer.

00:20:32.605 --> 00:20:33.165
I don't know why.

00:20:33.348 --> 00:20:35.200
I don't have a clue, to be real with you.

00:20:40.507 --> 00:20:40.960
But all I know is that God is a good God and the devil's a bad devil.

00:20:40.960 --> 00:20:43.589
And that's where I stay.

00:20:43.589 --> 00:20:54.570
I stay on God's side, and I don't sit there trying to have an arrogant ego, going, 'Well, why didn't you see this?

00:20:54.570 --> 00:20:56.220
' I don't know.

00:20:56.220 --> 00:20:57.360
I don't know.

00:20:57.360 --> 00:20:59.379
It wasn't meant for me to see.

00:20:59.379 --> 00:21:01.080
I don't see everything.

00:21:16.159 --> 00:21:16.419
There are a lot of things even in my own life.

00:21:16.419 --> 00:21:19.093
That's called God working with an imperfect vessel.

00:21:19.093 --> 00:21:25.360
He has a perfect message going through an imperfect vessel, and the pipe sometimes can get clogged.

00:21:30.319 --> 00:21:30.479
And He tells us, 'I need you to come up higher.

00:21:32.459 --> 00:21:32.729
I need you to come up higher, with the fire.

00:21:47.627 --> 00:21:48.053
I need you to sit at my throne.

00:21:48.053 --> 00:21:51.324
I need you to be a part of this glorious outpouring.

00:21:51.324 --> 00:21:54.799
Brandon, I need you to die to self more.

00:21:54.799 --> 00:21:57.020
I need you to rise up.

00:21:57.020 --> 00:22:00.187
' And so that's where we are right now.

00:22:00.187 --> 00:22:02.320
We're a work in progress.

00:22:02.320 --> 00:22:05.960
Every single one of us, we're a work in progress.

00:22:05.960 --> 00:22:08.663
So we give all the glory to Jesus.

00:22:08.663 --> 00:22:11.989
But I just want you to know that so much ignorance...

00:22:13.400 --> 00:22:13.653
I know hurting people hurt others.

00:22:13.653 --> 00:22:15.181
That's what Diana said.

00:22:15.181 --> 00:22:19.040
Hurting people hurt others and they don't get it.

00:22:19.040 --> 00:22:21.520
But we want to love you from afar.

00:22:35.349 --> 00:22:35.577
I'm just going to love you.

00:22:46.579 --> 00:22:46.789
Let me bless you out here as you throw rocks at me.

00:22:46.789 --> 00:22:47.840
So, God bless y'all.

00:22:47.840 --> 00:22:48.663
Let's pray.

00:22:48.663 --> 00:22:52.020
Let's get serious about this.

00:22:52.020 --> 00:22:55.462
I just wanted to address that a little bit.

00:22:55.462 --> 00:22:57.940
Maybe I should have, maybe I shouldn't have.

00:22:57.940 --> 00:22:59.300
I don't know.

00:22:59.300 --> 00:23:04.853
But I just felt it in my heart to do it because some things annoyed me.

00:23:04.853 --> 00:23:05.760
I just go, 'Whatever, man.

00:23:05.760 --> 00:23:07.300
' But praise God for people.

00:23:19.680 --> 00:23:19.920
I know people are just hurting.

00:23:19.920 --> 00:23:20.640
All right.

